author: struberg
msg: EXTCDI-286 remove tabs and fix indentation

author: struberg
msg: EXTCDI-286 prevent deploying of our examples
There are a few reasons to _not_ deploy examples:
* they contain jars in WEB-INF/lib which
can cause legal issues under certain conditions
* they are not part of our core distribution

author: stsp
msg: (svn_cl__conflict_handler): Show all conflicted paths relative to the current
directory instead of showing absolute paths. This was already done for
tree conflicts and is now done for text and property conflicts, too.

author: stsp
msg: (svn_cl__resolve): When determining the default depth to use, test
opt_state->accept_which against the correct type of constant.
Makes 'svn resolve' recursive by default, as intended, rather than
always using depth 'emtpy'. I introduced this problem in last-minute
